java.lang.Cloneable, Copy<NodeVisitor>
public class DeadCodeEliminator
extends DataFlow<DeadCodeEliminator.DataFlowItem>
Visitor which performs dead code elimination. (Note that "dead code" is not unreachable code, but is actually code that has no effect.)
